<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>OTP Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f6f9fc;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #eee;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      color: #007bff;
    }
    .otp {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2d3748;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 25px 0;
      padding: 12px;
      background: #f1f5f9;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px dashed #ccc;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #e63946;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="header">OTP Verification</h2>
    <p>Hello <b><%= name %></b>,</p>
    <p>We received a request to verify your email: <b><%= email %></b>.</p>

    <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) is:</p>
    <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>

    <p>This OTP is valid for <span class="highlight">5 minutes</span>.  
       Please do not share it with anyone.</p>

    <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this message.</p>

    <div class="footer">&copy; MatirPay. All rights reserved.</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
